NEYRELLE and the PLAYER stand a distance away from Donan and Lorath. Neyrelle stands TENSE with frustration, her one hand clenched tight. She is near DESPONDENT.

Neyrelle GASPS and STEPS BACK hesitantly as MEPHISTO himself steps through the portal in his WOLF FORM. The Player is WARY. 

Mephisto begins to CIRCLE the pair.
The Player steps in front of Neyrelle defensively. She peeks out with morbid curiosity, looking back and forth between Mephisto and the Player.
Neyrelle places her hand over her mouth and GASPS as she comes to the realization.
Mephisto wearily sits as she continues, angrilly.
Mephisto gestures to the portal with his head.
